<section>

<title>Setningstypar</title>
<p> Vi bruker tre slags setninger:</p>
<table>
<tr><td><strong>Forkorting</strong></td><td><strong>Setningstype</strong></td><td><strong>Døme</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>STA</strong></td><td>Fortellende setning (statement)</td><td>Sii ráhkadedje muohtaádjáid ja muohtaeŋgeliid.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>QUE</strong></td><td>Spørjesetning (question)</td><td>Boađát go odne?</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>COM</strong></td><td>Bydesetning (command)</td><td>Buvtte gáfe!</td></tr>

</table>

</section>


<section>
<title>Setningsledd</title>
<p>Vi bruker desse setningsledda:</p>
<table>
<tr><td><strong>Forkorting</strong></td><td><strong>Setningsledd</strong></td><td><strong>Døme</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>S</strong></td><td>Subjekt</td><td><em>Min nieiddat </em> leat čeahpit. Bahádahkki <em> son </em> lea! De dáhpáhuvai, <em>ahte rievvár bođii.</em></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>P</strong></td><td>Verbal (predikator)</td><td>Min nieiddat<em> leat </em> čeahpit.<em> Ale mana!</em> Don <em>galggat</em> jaska <em>veallát</em>.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Od</strong></td><td>Objekt</td><td>Bija<em>  buori dola</em>.<em> Maid</em>  Máret áigu oastit? Dieđát go <em>goas mis lea čoahkkin?</em></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>A</strong></td><td>Advearbial</td><td>Lávvui gullá<em>  maid </em> uvssot. Doai leahppi<em>  áŋgirit </em> lohkan sámegiela<em>  olles dálvvi</em>. Nieida lei<em>  skuvllas</em>. <em>Jus dieđášin</em>, de dajašin.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>HAB</strong></td><td>Habitatiiva</td><td><em>Mus </em> leat ustibat.<em> Min bussás </em> leat alit čalmmit.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>fC</strong></td><td>Predikativ</td><td>Min bussás leat<em>  alit čalmmit</em>. Gáttis ledje<em> olbmot</em>.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Cs</strong></td><td>Subjeaktpredikativ</td><td>Min nieiddat leat<em>  čeahpit</em>. </td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Co</strong></td><td>Objektpredikativ</td><td>Son oaččui dan<em>  luoikkasin</em>. Gáhkuid son ráhkada<em>  hui buriid</em>.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Cp</strong></td><td>Predikativpredikativ</td><td>Mus leat gieđat<em>  nu galbmasat</em>.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>CO</strong></td><td>Koordinator</td><td><em> Muhto </em> Parkera gal deavččastetne.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>SUB</strong></td><td>Subordinator</td><td><em>Jus</em> dieđášin,<em>  de  </em>dajašin. Son lea viššaleabbo<em>  go </em> mun.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>PART</strong></td><td>Partikkel</td><td>Boađát<em>  go </em> odne?</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>VOC</strong></td><td>Vokativ</td><td><em>Gilette,  </em> boađe donge!</td></tr>
</table>

<p>Vi bruker desse forkortingane ved sideordning:</p>

<table>
<tr><td><strong>Forkorting</strong></td><td><strong>Sideordningsledd</strong></td><td><strong>Døme</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>CO</strong></td><td>Koordinator</td><td>Sii ráhkadedje muohtaádjáid<em>  ja</em> muohtaeŋgeliid.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>CJT</strong></td><td>Konjunkt </td><td>Sii ráhkadedje<em>  muohtaádjáid</em> ja<em>  muohtaeŋgeliid</em>.</td></tr>
</table>
</section>

